{"id":62082,"date":"2021-08-09T15:15:34","date_gmt":"2021-08-09T14:15:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=62082"},"modified":"2022-09-20T11:49:28","modified_gmt":"2022-09-20T09:49:28","slug":"bordeaux","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/bordeaux\/","title":{"rendered":"11 Best Things To Do in Bordeaux (Wine Capital of France)"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">Things to do in Bordeaux, France<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Jump out of bed, hire a bike, and get ready for a few days of sightseeing in the charming French city of Bordeaux! (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/bordeaux-all-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Click to explore all the hotel options in the city<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121429\/Bordeaux5.jpg\" alt=\"bordeaux france things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"bordeaux france things to do\" class=\"wp-image-62483 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121429\/Bordeaux5.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121429\/Bordeaux5-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121429\/Bordeaux5-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121429\/Bordeaux5-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121429\/Bordeaux5-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121429\/Bordeaux5-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/0912