lock-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>5. Saturday Market at St. Michael&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Is there anything better than an authentic French market? The Saturday market at St Michael is no exception! The buzzing market sits around the basilica and is the perfect way to kick-start your weekend in Bordeaux. Find everything you&#x2019;d expect from a farmers market: locally sourced fruit, veggies, meats, and cheeses. It&#x2019;s a colorful and atmospheric way to enjoy the city and a beautiful setting to see the cathedral.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/bordeaux-all-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Explore all the hotels options in Bordeaux<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121645\/Bordeaux14.jpg\" alt=\"Saturday Market at St. Michael&#xA0; bordeaux things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Saturday Market at St. Michael&#xA0; bordeaux things to do\" class=\"wp-image-62499 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121645\/Bordeaux14.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121645\/Bordeaux14-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121645\/Bordeaux14-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhai