 one of the most striking buildings in Bordeaux: a futuristic structure that can be seen shimmering in the distance with its glass and aluminum panels. The building is home to a museum that&#x2019;s dedicated to Bordeaux&#x2019;s love of wine, and it&#x2019;s designed to represent the swirling of wine in a glass.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09135422\/bordeaux18.jpg\" alt=\"bordeaux france things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"bordeaux france things to do\" class=\"wp-image-62515 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09135422\/bordeaux18.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09135422\/bordeaux18-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09135422\/bordeaux18-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09135422\/bordeaux18-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09135422\/bordeaux18-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09135422\/bordeaux18-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09135422\/bordeaux18-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09135422\/bordeaux18-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09135422\/bordeaux18-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09135422\/bordeaux18-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09135422\/bordeaux18-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\