rhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/62082&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12094724\/bordeaux-france-things-to-do4.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12094724\/bordeaux-france-things-to-do4-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12094724\/bordeaux-france-things-to-do4-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"11 Best Things To Do in Bordeaux (Wine Capital of France)\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>10. Wander Through the City&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Bordeaux is so vibrant and varied that it&#x2019;s a pleasure to just spend the day walking from neighborhood to neighborhood, eating, people watching, and drinking the wine that makes Bordeaux so famous. If you&#x2019;re interested to learn more about Bordeaux or find secret spots, it&#x2019;s worth booking a walking tour with an official guide who will be able to tell you everything you need to know.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/bordeaux-walking-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book a walking tour easily here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121446\/Bordeaux6-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-62485 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121446\/Bordeaux6-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121446\/Bordeaux6-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121446\/Bordeaux6-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121446\/Bordeaux6-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121446\/Bordeaux6-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121446\/Bordeaux6-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121446\/Bordeaux6-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/09121446\/Bordeaux6-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\