chways. In fact, there are 17 arches in total that rise and fall across the water. The bridge is closed to cars and is only used by pedestrians and cyclists. Because of this, it&#x2019;s a great place to enjoy views across the river and of both sides of the city.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Cross Pont de Pierre at night, to watch the sun go down over the city. At night, romantic lamp lights light up the bridge.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12085115\/bordeaux35.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"266\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-62597 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12085115\/bordeaux35.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12085115\/bordeaux35-800x473.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12085115\/bordeaux35-1080x639.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12085115\/bordeaux35-450x266.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12085115\/bordeaux35-30x18.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12085115\/bordeaux35-163x96.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/12085115\/bordeaux35-304x180.jpg