Bordeaux<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bordeaux is full of gorgeous boutique guesthouses, luxury hotels, and traditional apartments. The best area to stay in is the historic center, where you can have easy access to all the beautiful sights. (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/bordeaux-all-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See all hotels in the city<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotel-de-tourny-bordeaux\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/03122725\/210966101-30x20.jpeg\" alt=\"Boutique H&#xF4;tel de Tourny\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/03122725\/210966101-450x300.jpeg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                        <div class=\"product__content-title\">Boutique H&#xF4;tel de Tourny<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/la-maison-odeia-bordeaux\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/03122717\/116861430-30x20.jpeg\" alt=\"La Maison Odeia\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2