 &#x2013; 130 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--restaurants\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Price per meal: 15 &#x2013; 40 USD \n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Transport: 5 &#x2013; 20 USD \/ day\n                    <\/li><\/ul><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Things to do in Bordeaux, France Jump out of bed, hire a bike, and get ready for a few days of sightseeing in the charming French city of Bordeaux! (Click to explore all the hotel options in the city) 1. Le Miroir d&#x2019;eau + Place de la Bourse Le Miroir d&#x2019;eau is one of the [&hellip;]","protected":false},"author":6,"featured_media":62475,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_relevanssi_hide_post":"","_relevanssi_pin_for_all":"","_relevanssi_pin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_unpin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_include_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_exclude_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_no_append":"","_relevanssi_related_not_related":"","_relevanssi_related_posts":"16664,16218,61673,19955,34927,15592"},"categories":[4750,2164,9],"tags":[78,66],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v19.3 (Yoast SEO v19.7.1) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Bordeaux, France: 11 Best Things To Do in 2021 \u00b7 Salt in our Hair<\/title>\n<meta name=\"descriptio